  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rollingford\" title=\"House Rollingford\"><img alt=\"House Rollingford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/50px-House_Rollingford.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/75px-House_Rollingford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/100px-House_Rollingford.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Herman Rollingford</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rollingford\" title=\"House Rollingford\"><img alt=\"House Rollingford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/50px-House_Rollingford.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/75px-House_Rollingford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/39/House_Rollingford.svg/100px-House_Rollingford.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Rollingford\" title=\"House Rollingford\">House Rollingford</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Herman Rollingford</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rollingford\" title=\"House Rollingford\">House Rollingford</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Herman_Rollingford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Herman accompanied Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Mooton\" title=\"Manfryd Mooton\">Manfryd Mooton</a> during his diplomatic mission to <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>. Herman was killed in a duel by a <a href=\"/index.php/Bravo\" title=\"Bravo\">bravo</a> who objected to the color of Herman's doublet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Herman_Rollingford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol clas